videos.headline: Liberty's attempt at trickery fails as Army intercepts the pass
videos.description: Liberty kicker Max Morgan attempts to fool Army with a pass instead of a kick, but his throw is intercepted by the Black Knights.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Liberty’s attempt at trickery fails as Army intercepts the pass) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murphy hauls in 34-yard pass for an Army touchdown
videos.description: Army's Christian Anderson connects with Braheam Murphy for a 34-yard touchdown to put the Black Knights on the board first vs. Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murphy hauls in 34-yard pass for an Army touchdown) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Army's Buchanan rushes 19 yards untouched for TD
videos.description: Jakobi Buchanan takes the ball 19 yards to the end zone for Army's second touchdown of the first half vs. Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Army’s Buchanan rushes 19 yards untouched for TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buchanan punches in a short TD for his second on the day
videos.description: Jakobi Buchanan takes the handoff and shoves his way across the plane for his second touchdown of the day for Army vs. Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buchanan punches in a short TD for his second on the day) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Buchanan scores his 3rd TD of the day
videos.description: Jakobi Buchanan punches in a short touchdown in the third quarter to pick up his third score of the game vs. Liberty.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Buchanan scores his 3rd TD of the day) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Frith pulls in a 14-yard TD for Liberty
videos.description: Noah Frith grabs a 14-yard pass from Malik Willis to give Liberty its first touchdown of the game in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Frith pulls in a 14-yard TD for Liberty) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Willis keeps it himself for 7-yard TD
videos.description: Malik Willis looks to throw the ball but then decides to tuck it and run into the end zone for a second Liberty touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Willis keeps it himself for 7-yard TD) 2021/11/27 ESHEET
